{"tid":2243431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12歲女童遭壓地 警改稱「截停」","createTime":"2020-10-14T17:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T21:07:16.000Z","uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"264aa7d6a1bab75022864ed116da1317a8062e29","tid":2243431,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T17:15:15.000Z","msg":"本月6日網民發起九龍遊行，其間一名聲稱在旺角買文具及顏料的12歲女童遭多名防暴警撲壓在地。警方起初形容以最低武力「制服」少女，惟近日回覆油尖旺區議員副主席余德寶時改稱「<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">截停</span></span>」。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱當時馬上安慰事主。警方「以最低所需武力將其制服」，調查後女童因違反限聚令被票控。惟警方數日前回覆余德寶稱，少女「可疑的舉措」令在場警員有必要以最低武力「截停」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5362063/org/576d2ff23ea05966d2808c0bd93c4e7a.jpg/PfTiFCvRe1DZfWlRy1AsXVWVI4N79kXJlZUYWJWVGFg?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5362063%2Forg%2F576d2ff23ea05966d2808c0bd93c4e7a.jpg%2FPfTiFCvRe1DZfWlRy1AsXVWVI4N79kXJlZUYWJWVGFg%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=9bfbb20b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"green\">警方表示，任何人如認為於警方處理事件時受不合理對待，可向投訴警察課投訴，會按既定程序公平公正處理。</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20200928/HK-gcc1_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Ftor%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20200928%2FHK-gcc1_r.htm&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyicpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=c3d1ffa1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20200928/HK-gcc1_r.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ac3258d29c2f69b981078f7486eea49bac7a5aa7","tid":2243431,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T17:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d344d895783f98787b8368475f551e490c3251c","tid":2243431,"uid":105691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T17:17:09.000Z","msg":"朱媛朱媛朱媛朱媛朱媛朱媛<br />\n<a href=\"https://